## 3. Design System

### 3.1 Design Tokens

```css
/* Backgrounds */
--bg: #0D1117;           /* Primary canvas/background */
--bg-secondary: #161B22;  /* Card, panel surfaces */
--bg-tertiary: #1C2333;   /* Button, elevated hover */
--bg-elevated: #1A1E2E;   /* Toast, dialog */

/* Foreground */
--fg: #E6EDF3;            /* Primary text */
--fg-secondary: #8B949E;  /* Secondary text, body copy */
--fg-tertiary: #484F58;   /* Captions, disabled */

/* Accent */
--accent: #7C3AED;        /* Primary accent (violet) */
--accent-hover: #8B5CF6;  /* Hover state */
--accent-soft: rgba(124,58,237,0.15); /* Subtle accent bg */
--accent-2: #DB2777;      /* Secondary accent (pink) */
--accent-2-soft: rgba(219,39,119,0.12);
--accent-3: #3B82F6;      /* Tertiary accent (blue) */
--accent-3-soft: rgba(59,130,246,0.1);

/* Semantic */
--green: #6A9955;
--border: #30363D;
--border-strong: #484F58;

/* Glass */
--glass-bg: rgba(13,17,23,0.88);
--glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
```

